  article#about
    h3: a(name="about") About Us
    p We help assess, mitigate, and refine fundraising operations, specializing in The Raiser's Edge&trade; and Crystal Reports&trade;.
    p We believe in specialized solutions. We are dedicated to working with your organization to discover what is needed and then create a solution that will work for you&mdash;all with minimal demands on your staff's valuable time.
    h3 Leadership Team
    section#leadership
      div
        img(src="images/Melody_McBeth.jpg", alt="photo", title="Melody McBeth")
        div
          h4
            a(href="mailto:melody.mcbeth@highlandfrs.com?subject=\"Website contact\"", target="_blank") Melody McBeth
            | - Principal
          p Melody has more than 15 years of experience in fundraising, almost 10 of which were spent in independent secondary school development. She has served as a solicitor, volunteer manager, event coordinator, the database/systems administrator and senior Crystal Reports&trade; architect, and as the Director of Advancement Services. Her work has been recognized by her peers, other consultants, and software manufacturers alike.
          p Before entering the development field, Melody served in the Armed Forces, managed various other businesses including a karate studio, and held state and local offices with the Pennsylvania Jaycees. Her cross industry experience has proven vital to formulating highly successful solutions to sticky data challenges.
          p Melody currently serves on the #[a(href="http://www.advserv.org/?page=Committees", target="_blank") Curriculum Committee, FundSvcs Committee, and chairs the Program Committee] with the #[a(href="http://www.advserv.org/", target="_blank") Association of Advancement Services Professionals].
          ul
            li: a(href="https://twitter.com/HighlandFRS", target="_blank")
                span.icon-twitter(title="twitter logo")
                | Follow @HighlandFRS on Twitter
            li: a(href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/melodymcbethhfrs", target="_blank")
                span.icon-linkedin(title="linkedin logo")
                | View Melody's profile on LinkedIn

      div
