        div
          h4
            a(href="http://www.waynecombs.com/", target="_blank") Dr. Wayne Combs
            | - Strategic Partner
          p Combs has more than 20 years of experience in fundraising and will be a key asset in Highland's capital and comprehensive campaign division. Combs' experience in performing organizational assessments, evaluating business systems and data management, applying process improvement techniques in advancement services, directing budget management, and supporting a $6 billion dollar campaign will augment the firm's current services.
          p Combs earned his Ed.D. in higher education administration at USC Rossier School of Education where he teaches doctoral courses in creativity, innovation and entrepreneurship.  He is actively involved in supporting the field of philanthropy as a #[a(href="http://www.advserv.org/?page=Committees", target="_blank") member of the board of directors] for the #[a(href="http://www.advserv.org/", target="_blank") Association of Advancement Services Professionals (AASP)] and as chair/faculty for the #[a(href="http://www.case.org/", target="_blank") Council for the Advancement and Support of Education (CASE)].
